title: BRIEF-Hewlett Packard Enterprise Says Marc Andreessen Notified Board He Will Not Seek Reelection At 2018 Annual Meeting Of Stockholders
text:
#Market News  18 AM / in 4 minutes BRIEF-Hewlett Packard Enterprise Says Marc Andreessen Notified Board He Will Not Seek Reelection At 2018 Annual Meeting Of Stockholders Reuters Staff 1 Min Read 
Feb 6 (Reuters) - Hewlett Packard Enterprise Co: 
* HEWLETT PACKARD ENTERPRISE SAYS ON FEB 1, MARC ANDREESSEN NOTIFIED BOARD HE WILL NOT SEEK REELECTION AT 2018 ANNUAL MEETING OF STOCKHOLDERS-SEC FILING Source text for Eikon: ( bit.ly/2GR7hwV ) Further company coverage:
